{"tid":2401533,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"叫我睇果錯條撚樣出黎","createTime":"2021-02-09T21:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T23:21:19.000Z","uid":254376,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"38899f1e7b422d064fd67d47294a010a5b6baccf","tid":2401533,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T21:03:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！！點解要咁對我？比啲咁既嘢我睇？晒左我幾十粒鐘不在話下，搞到我喊到仆街仲係人黎？我話要輕鬆啲啊，唔撚係整到我喊啊！屌！男人老狗比你搞到我咁....點解啊......雖然個結局係我要既，但點解中間要咁樣？點解一定要有人犧牲？好撚心痛....睇完個結局都唔方開心得去邊...好撚慘...一見到男豬一次又一次同結衣既感情發展，個心就好撚唔舒服，雖然好想男豬同雪乃一齊，但都好想結衣爭返口氣，套嘢真係好仆街...睇到我喊左成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚好睇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"h